%h1 The RailsBridge Team

%p
  The team of people that make RailsBridge successful is too large to include here.
  Each RailsBridge chapter is run by a team of dedicated volunteers, and the RailsBridge board
  exists primarily to assist those chapter leaders in running workshops and creating communities.
  All members of the RailsBridge board serve on committees that support cross-chapter concerns, like
  finance, chapter outreach, fundraising, and communications. The board relies on the
  input of the RailsBridge Advisory Board when making decisions. To learn more about how the board works, check out the
  #{ link_to "RailsBridge Board Charter", "https://github.com/railsbridge/board#railsbridge-board-charter", target: "_blank", class: 'inline-link' }.

